public class LandUseType
extends AbstractCityObjectType

Type describing the class for Land Use in all LOD. LandUse objects describe areas of the earthâ€™s surface dedicated to a specific land use. The geometry must consist of 3-D surfaces. As subclass of _CityObject, a LandUse inherits all attributes and relations, in particular an id, names, external references, and generalization relations.
